      "name": "Bench-scale hemolysis index comparison — FDA generic centrifugal pump",
      "description": "Relative hemolysis index (RHI) predicted by CFD compared against in-vitro measurements across 5 operating points. All predicted RHI values fell within experimental uncertainty bounds. Mean absolute error 6.3%. Acceptance criterion RH < 1 satisfied at all conditions."
