      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Commercial CFD solver with documented V&V history and version-controlled configuration files sufficient for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 used under institutional software QA protocol. Solver version locked and configuration files archived in institutional repository. Release notes and known-issues register reviewed; no open issues affect rotating-machinery hemolysis predictions."
